nternal\" href=\"#id17\">1.0.9 (2010/10/12)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id18\">1.0.8 (2010/08/11)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id19\">1.0.7 (2010/08/06)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id20\">1.0.6 (2010/08/05)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id21\">1.0.5 (2010/06/12)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id22\">1.0.4 (2010/06/10)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id23\">1.0.3 (2010/06/07)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id24\">1.0.2 (2010/05/25)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id25\">1.0.1 (2010/05/19)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id26\">1.0.0 (2010/05/10)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id27\">0.9.0 (2010/04/14)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id28\">0.4.0 (2010/03/28)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id29\">0.3.3 (2010/03/27)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id30\">0.3.2 (2010/03/26)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id31\">0.3.0 (2010/03/26)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id32\">0.2.0 (2010/03/10)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#id33\">0.1.0 (2010/02/10)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../../../authoring/supplementary/", "title": "Supplementary information"}, "metatags": ""}